TextEng: Who are you? My name is <FullName>.
We must speak of the werewolves.
Who you be? Me is <FullName>.
We gots to talk 'bout werewolves.
Goodbye.
Perhaps you need some assistance?

Me needs directions in town.
Can you point me in the direction of an inn?

I'll need someplace to buy equipment.
Let me ask about something else.
Me need inn to go to.
Me cannot find temple. Where one be?
Text: 나 신전 못 찾아. 어디 있어?

TextEng: Me needs buy stuff like weapon and armor.

TextEng: Me think of different thing to ask.
Tell me what you would have me do.
Me not knowing what me is doing to help. You say now?

TextEng: Who is this Ander you mention?
Where can I get the weapons to fight werewolves?

TextEng: I will do this for you.
Me wonders who Ander is.
Me need special weapons fighting werewolves, yeah?

TextEng: Me can do this.
I have some more questions about this job.
Text: 이 일에 대해 몇 가지 더 물어볼게요.

TextEng: Me got some questions 'bout job.
Who is this Ander you mention?
Where can I get the weapons to fight werewolves?

TextEng: Where will I find these afflicted boys?

TextEng: Me wonders who Ander is.
Me need special weapons fighting werewolves, yeah?

TextEng: I've some questions about the boys you wish cured.
Text: 치료하고 싶으신 소년들에 대해 몇 가지 물어볼게요.

Text: 나 치료하고 싶은 소년들 관련 질문 있어.

TextEng: Remind me what you needed help with...
Text: 무엇을 도와드려야 하는지 다시 말씀해 주시겠어요...

TextEng: You reminds me what job you was wanting me do, yuh?
Text: 너 내가 해야 할 일 뭐였는지 다시 말해 줘?

TextEng: I found Urth. Here is his ring.
What services does Tyr provide?
Text: 티르께서 어떤 도움을 주실 수 있죠?

TextEng: Me wanting know what Tyr gives me.
Text: 나 티르가 뭐 줄 수 있는지 알고 싶어.

TextEng: I'd like to make a purchase from the temple.
Me wants to buy stuff from temple.
Can you tell me anything about Bran?
Text: 브랜에 대해 뭔가 알려주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: What do you know of Geth?
Where might I find Urth?
Do you know where Sir Karathis is?
Could I speak with his family?
I know the true identity of the Black Wolf, Neurik. It is Alhelor.
Text: 검은 늑대의 정체를 알아요, 뉴릭. 바로 알헬러예요.

TextEng: Me knows who Black Wolf be. It be Alhelor!
Text: 나 검은 늑대 누군지 알아. 알헬러야!

TextEng: I will do as you ask.
Me will do as you asks.
Will there be a reward for this task, too?
Me can gets more gold, yeah?
Text: 나 금화 더 받을 수 있어?

TextEng: I cannot accept this job now.
Text: 지금은 이 일을 맡을 수 없어요.

TextEng: Me not take this job, no.
What exactly am I to do, again?
Text: 정확히 제가 뭘 해야 하는 거죠?.

TextEng: Me not remembers... what me to do, again?
Text: 나 기억 안 나... 나 뭐 하는 거였어?

TextEng: Alhelor is dead. I have his tooth, here.
Text: 알헬러는 죽었어요. 여기 그의 이빨이 있습니다.

TextEng: Me gots Alhelor tooth, yuh? He be dead.
Text: 나 알헬러 이빨 가졌어. 그 죽었어.

TextEng: Alhelor yet lives, so far as I know.
Text: 제가 아는 한 알헬러는 아직 살아 있어요.

TextEng: Alhelor still alive, so far as me knows.
Text: 나 아는 한 알헬러 아직 살아 있어.

TextEng: Thank you for this. Farewell.
Bye bye. Thanks you, mister.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Port Llast can thank me better than this, aye?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 라스트 항구는 이것보다 더 나은 감사를 할 수 있지 않나요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Port Llast spends more to thank me than this, yuh?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 라스트 항구 이것보다 감사 더 많이 해야 하는 거 아냐?

TextEng: I killed Alhelor. Give me more gold, or you're next.
Text: 알헬러를 죽였어요. 금화를 더 주세요. 안 그러면 다음은 당신입니다.

TextEng: Me wants more gold. Me can kills you next like Alhelor!
Text: 나 금화 더 원해. 나 알헬러처럼 너도 죽일 수 있어!

TextEng: I found Bran. Here is his ring.
I found Geth. Here is his ring.
I found all three of them. Here are their rings.
Text: 셋 모두 찾았어요. 여기 그들의 반지예요.

TextEng: Me finds all three. Here is rings for you.
Text: 나 셋 다 찾았어. 여기 반지들.

TextEng: Me finds Urth. See, here his ring.
Text: 나 어스 찾았어. 여기 그 반지.

TextEng: Me finds Bran. See, here his ring.
Text: 나 브랜 찾았어. 여기 그 반지.

TextEng: Me finds Geth. See, here his ring.
Text: 나 게스 찾았어. 여기 그 반지.

TextEng: Me looks for Bran. You know stuff?
Text: 나 브랜 찾아. 너 뭐 알아?

TextEng: Me maybe gets clues for where Geth is?
Text: 나 게스 어디 있는지 단서 얻을 수 있어?

TextEng: Where Urth be? You know?
Where me should look for Sir Karathis, you think?
I've had some success in finding the boys, actually.
Text: 사실 소년들을 찾는 데 약간 성공했어요.

TextEng: Me finds out stuff about werewolf boys, yuh.
Text: 나 늑대인간 소년들 관련해서 뭔가 알아냈어.

TextEng: Why must I use a magical portal to enter your temple?
Text: 왜 신전에 들어가려면 마법 차원문을 써야 하는 거죠?

TextEng: Let me ask about something else.
Me can ask other thing now?
Text: 나 이제 다른 거 물어볼 수 있어?

TextEng: Let's talk about something different.
Me changes subject now, yuh?
Let me ask about something else.
Me ask different thing now.
Let me ask about something different.
Me asks different question instead, okay?
I will find them for you.
Me finds kids. Worry not!
I've not yet found Karathis or the Black Wolf.
Text: 아직 카라디스나 검은 늑대를 못 찾았어요.

TextEng: Me no find Karathis or Black Wolfie yet.
Text: 나 아직 카라디스나 검은 늑대 못 찾았어.

TextEng: Tell me more about Karathis and this Black Wolf.
Text: 카라디스와 검은 늑대에 대해 더 말씀해 주세요.

TextEng: You tells me more 'bout Karathis and Black Wolf.
Text: 너 카라디스랑 검은 늑대 관련해서 더 말해 줘.

TextEng: What has been happening in Port Llast?
Text: 라스트 항구에서 무슨 일이 있었던 거죠?

TextEng: What happens in town?
Why me need use magic portal thing to enter temple?
Text: 왜 나 신전 들어가려면 마법 차원문 같은 거 써야 해?

TextEng: That makes sense.
Oh. Okay.
Me needs healing.
I need healing.
Me speaks to family, maybe?
